# Project Context

## Tech Stack
- **UI Framework**: shadcn-vue (already installed)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS (already installed)
- **Icons**: Lucide Vue (already installed)

## Coding Conventions
- When creating UI components, use shadcn-vue components
- Use Tailwind CSS classes for styling
- Use Lucide icons for any icon requirements
- Do not ask for confirmation when using these technologies - they are the project standards

## Component Library
Use shadcn-vue components from `@/components/ui/` for common UI patterns like:
- Button
- Input
- Card
- Dialog
- Toast/sonner (vue-sonner)
- Form components
- etc.
